text: Émilie () is a French female given name. It is the female version of the male name Émile. Spelled Emilie, it is used in several countries. This is a unique name (not in the top 1000 newborn names in the US in 2021). ==People named Emilie== * Emilie Autumn, American musician * Emilie de Ravin (born 1981), Australian actress * Emilie Béatrice Epaye, Central African politician ==References==
title: Émilie
